WEBVTT

00:01.222 --> 00:03.735
- Previously on Wrecked...
- Danny, get away from me.

00:03.737 --> 00:05.204
I'm not gonna leave you.
You're my friend.

00:05.239 --> 00:07.748
I am not your friend! We are
just stuck here together!

00:07.749 --> 00:10.750
