00:21.663 --> 00:23.696
- What do I do?
- What about Owen's boat?

00:23.732 --> 00:25.231
- Emma!
- What?

00:25.266 --> 00:27.667
Oh, my God. There she is! Emma!

00:27.702 --> 00:30.569
I'll be fine! Go back! I'm sorry!

00:30.605 --> 00:32.570
- I got to go back for Danny.
- I'm going with you.

00:33.312 --> 00:35.341
Let's go save this island.

00:36.808 --> 00:38.778
Look! They're getting away!

00:42.253 --> 00:43.941
Holy shit!

00:43.942 --> 00:44.884
Oh, my God!

00:45.136 --> 00:46.936
The son of a bitch shot me!

00:49.707 --> 00:53.009
No one else leaves my island!

00:53.044 --> 00:54.911
Do you hear me?!

00:54.946 --> 00:57.013
No one!

00:57.048 --> 00:58.647
Todd! Todd!

00:58.683 --> 01:01.117
- Step back!
- Todd!

01:01.152 --> 01:02.718
What are you doing?!

01:02.754 --> 01:04.720
