01:31.582 --> 01:34.150
I am so sorry, everyone.

01:34.185 --> 01:38.087
Oh, Steve has my gun.

01:44.190 --> 01:44.794
Danny.

01:44.829 --> 01:47.230
Really good to see you, Steve.
How are things?

01:49.000 --> 01:49.914
