02:08.586 --> 02:10.820
You know what? Forget it.
Last-word privileges revoked.

02:10.854 --> 02:12.055
This is bullshit!

02:12.090 --> 02:14.490
Guys, we don't have to
take this from him.

02:14.525 --> 02:16.725
We can fight back.

02:16.761 --> 02:17.927
Danny's right!

02:17.963 --> 02:19.628
Steve should go in the pit.

02:19.664 --> 02:20.997
Careful, Jess.

02:21.032 --> 02:22.231
You shot Todd.

02:22.267 --> 02:24.834
