02:24.869 --> 02:26.936
Those were your rules, Steve.

02:26.972 --> 02:28.171
Grab him!

02:29.774 --> 02:33.176
S-Seriously, guys? No one?

02:33.211 --> 02:35.511
Grab me!

02:36.548 --> 02:38.848
Come on, guys! Oh, come on!

02:38.883 --> 02:40.749
Yeah, okay, real big men

02:40.785 --> 02:42.551
