06:21.850 --> 06:23.616
Oh, my God. Did he just kill Turdhole?!

06:23.652 --> 06:25.251
All right. We got to signal the ship.

06:25.286 --> 06:26.519
We got to start a fire.

06:26.554 --> 06:28.521
No, no, no, no! He's lost his damn mind!

06:28.556 --> 06:30.356
