07:13.768 --> 07:15.768
- Ah, it's nothing.
- Look at your love handles.

07:15.804 --> 07:17.603
It's getting crazy infected.

07:17.638 --> 07:19.405
- You mean my ab?
- Oh, my God.

07:19.440 --> 07:20.940
