07:26.715 --> 07:30.349
You got to save Jess, all right?

07:30.384 --> 07:31.684
Promise me.

07:31.720 --> 07:32.919
I promise.

07:32.954 --> 07:36.989
No one deserves to be thrown in a pit.

07:37.605 --> 07:40.639
Damn! Goose bumpers!

07:40.674 --> 07:42.241
- Right?
- Yeah, that sounded hardcore.

07:42.276 --> 07:44.143
Okay. I'm gonna go.

07:44.522 --> 07:46.689
Roger? Roger?

07:46.725 --> 07:48.224
You got to let us out of here, man.

07:48.259 --> 07:50.560
You're not going anywhere
unless Steve says.

07:50.595 --> 07:53.596
Roger, the boat is right
out there, okay?!

07:53.631 --> 07:54.997
Don't you want to go home on that boat?!

07:55.032 --> 07:56.632
Look at me. Look at my face!

07:56.668 --> 07:59.569
I can't go back to the real
world looking like this.

07:59.604 --> 08:01.571
Come on, man. Your face
...Your face is fine.

08:01.606 --> 08:03.305
It doesn't look like... like sausage.

08:03.341 --> 08:04.707
