I'll do it again.

08:08.980 --> 08:10.513
Oh, God! Oh, what the shit?

08:13.985 --> 08:15.485
Okay.

08:15.520 --> 08:17.253
We got to get you guys the
hell out of here. Come on!

08:19.409 --> 08:20.423
Hey, Pack.

08:20.458 --> 08:21.624
- Get back!
- Hey.

08:21.659 --> 08:23.058
What are you doing here?

08:23.094 --> 08:25.528
Hey, man, the boat is leaving, okay?

08:25.563 --> 08:27.162
Come on. Come on, don't
you want to go home?

08:27.198 --> 08:31.066
