from that crazy motherfu...

08:53.640 --> 08:55.257
Welcome home, Florence.

08:58.182 --> 08:59.429
You can't shoot all of us!

08:59.464 --> 09:00.630
Everybody, run!

09:00.665 --> 09:02.732
Wait! We're running or not?

09:02.767 --> 09:04.133
Okay!

09:08.339 --> 09:09.505
Well, come on, Karen!

09:09.541 --> 09:11.273
Don't just stand there! Get them!

09:11.309 --> 09:14.076
Shit, shit, shit!

09:15.713 --> 09:18.414
Don't you want to get rescued, huh?

09:18.450 --> 09:22.017
Owen, I've done things
...unspeakable things.

09:22.053 --> 09:23.352
I'm a monster!

09:23.387 --> 09:25.287
Yeah, you are!

09:25.323 --> 09:27.089
Hey, buddy, listen to me.

09:27.124 --> 09:29.459
Whatever you did, it can't be that bad.

09:29.494 --> 09:30.660
