09:54.053 --> 09:55.719
Really?

09:57.190 --> 09:59.290
It's totally normal.

09:59.325 --> 10:03.160
So, people won't think I'm
insane like... like Steve said?

10:03.196 --> 10:04.695
I don't think so.

10:04.730 --> 10:06.430
